data.text:
2007 Canadian-American Association

The 2007 season was the Canadian-American Association's 13th, and 10 teams competed in the league that year. The Nashua Pride won the 2007 Canadian-American Association championship.

Level: Independent

Season Began: Thursday, May 24, 2007

Season Ended: Monday, September 3, 2007
